ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether the asserted set of linkages are considered to be "in effect".

ivardefs.name: author
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the user or organization responsible for asserting the linkages as well as the user or organization who establishes the context in which the nature of each linkage is evaluated.

ivardefs.name: item_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies which record considered as the reference to the same real-world occurrence as well as how the items should be evaluated within the collection of linked items.

properties.desc: Identifies two or more records (resource instances) that refer to the same real-world "occurrence".
